 color="000000">5 points for a complete game or</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">7 points for a shutout complete game</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">10 points for a no-hitter</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">3 points for a quality start if not a complete game (6 or more IP, 3 or fewer earned runs allowed)</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position